<br>
I would say that someone spamming NASCAR results into the shout channel or wandering around DEWD SOW PLZ...   DEWD SOW PLZ... is griefing within the context of THIS SERVER. They are disrupting the play of roleplayers and this server is for roleplayers. The same would not apply on Morell-Thule where I am now.<br>
<br>
Someone that says REZ HIM PLZ is unthinkingly and rudely disrupting the environment, but they don't have to babble some huge blurt about &quot;Proud Priest of Brell, save my noble companion from the ravages of the Dark Domains.&quot; But geez, how about &quot;Could you resurrect my friend&quot; instead of &quot;REZ PLZ&quot; <br>
<br>
Likewise, I think that as a roleplayer, my ability to complain about non-RP behavior on other servers goes way down with the creation of this server. <p>Numtini Lightheart <br>
