I am a little worried about the White Cloaks coming to this server with premonitions that those who don't fit the template well enough will be persecuted.  Sure, if someone harasses you, spams a zone with d00dspeak, feel free to /petition and/or /ignore.  But, as it was put before, if someone is minding their own business, not being an &quot;anti-roleplayer,&quot; then we don't have any beef with them.  There's no harm from their existence.<br>
